\cot\theta + \tan \theta = x
\sec \theta - \cos \theta = y
\left(x^2 y + xy^2\right)^{2/3}
\cot \theta
\frac{1}{\tan \theta}
\sec \theta
\left(x^2 y + xy^2\right)^{2/3}=\left(xy(x + y)\right)^{2/3}
xy=\frac{\sin \theta}{\cos^2 \theta}
x+y=\frac{1+\sin^3 \theta}{\sin \theta\cos \theta}
xy(x+y)=\frac{1+\sin^3 \theta}{\cos^3 \theta}
\left(xy(x + y)\right)^{2/3}=\frac{(1+\sin^3 \theta)^{2/3}}{\cos^2 \theta}
